Copyright 2019- Universität Hamburg  

Copyright 2009-2018 University of Ljubljana, Faculty of Mathematics and Physics (UL-FMF). 
Development of the MODES software version 1.0 as an open-access tool at UL-FMF was funded 
by the European Research Council, grant agreement no. 280153, 2012-2016.

The computation of the Hough harmonics and the vertical structure functions in the terrain-following 
sigma coordinate was written after the original code from the National Center for Atmospheric Research 
(NCAR), Boulder, CO, USA, originally developed by Akira Kasahara. 


